To install the please run:
`yarn`

and then:
`yarn start`


The location of each file can be found in the following path:
* Navigation bar: `src/layout/common/nav`
* Img comoponent: `src/layout/common/img.js`
* First section:  `/src/pages/components/home/welcome`
* Second section: `/src/pages/components/home/ourStory`
* third section(masonry layout): `/src/pages/components/home/treatments`
